des:
Listen to an adventure-themed story series with sound effects. Get ready for laughs and giggles with your thinking hat on, reflect on issues affecting gizmo geeks of either sex, are we a different species, reflect on this question, as we try to adopt to the more normal species, maybe gizmos are what we need....
In this series, the first episode is called, The Translator Episode. Listen on to reflect on the dreams in a scanner pen, the culture people in the circuits, reflect on whether android is similar?
